s
related to its ongoing business practices, Neon is generally permitted to r=
ecoup all actual, third-party costs and expenses related to the exercise of=
 its rights granted to films across its library, which necessarily includes=
 its costs and expenses to defend those rights.=E2=80=9D</li><br/><li><i>Su=
