x; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">The Regency saga be=
gan four decades ago with Arnon Milchan=E2=80=99s mysterious entry into Hol=
lywood=E2=80=94which has long puzzled the press, since he rarely gives inte=
rviews. Milchan, whose past included brokering clandestine arms deals for I=
srael, once <u><a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnV=
DJ4Z1lEQUt2UktxclJLZ0dRVWZSaHhGdGcxVlFjNW5HWFpBOD0iLCJocmVmIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93=
