XJtPWY2YzYwNjE3ZGE0MmFiZDEyYSIsImludGVybmFsIjoiZjZjNjA2MTdkYTQyYWJkMTJhIiwi=
bGlua19pZCI6OTM5OTgzfQ/f4d72b7f6708afd154175845babd994ca68389216529cc339356=
2202df6f421c" style=3D"color:#d40000;text-decoration:none;font-weight:bold"=
 class=3D"sdf">described</a></u> his younger self as a James
Bond figure. As for how this former Israeli intelligence officer caught his=
 big break, I discovered the answer in a deposition he gave where he recall=
ed getting a serendipitous phone call in the early =E2=80=9980s from <b>Rob=
ert De Niro</b>, who was researching a potential film. The actor had heard =
that Milchan was connected to <b>Moshe Dayan</b>, a storied Israeli general=
 during the 1948 Arab-Israeli War. This prompted a trip to Israel by De Nir=
o and <b>Harvey Keitel</b>. Soon after, <b>Jack Nicholson</b> also expresse=
d interest in the film rights to Dayan=E2=80=99s story, setting off what Mi=
lchan described as =E2=80=9Can avalanche of movie stars=E2=80=9D at his doo=
r.<br/><br/>Though the Dayan project never materialized, Milchan had gotten=
 a taste of Hollywood. In Israel, De Niro showed him the script for <i>The =
King of Comedy,</i> leading him to become a producer on the <b>Martin Scors=
ese</b> film. Milchan named his company after the Regency Hotel in New York=
, where he first set up shop and built
formidable ties with Hollywood=E2=80=99s elite, including <b>Richard Dreyfu=
ss</b> and <b>Sydney Pollack</b>. A friendship with Murdoch proved to be on=
e of his most significant associations. Murdoch=E2=80=99s 20th Century Fox =
eventually took a 20 percent stake in Regency, for $200 million, and began =
distributing many of its films, including Oscar winners <i>12 Years a Slave=
</i>, <i>Birdman</i>, and <i>The Revenant</i>.<br/><br/>But Regency lost a =
crucial ally when Murdoch sold Fox=E2=80=99s studio assets to Disney in 201=
8. Around the same time, Milchan was distancing himself from what he now re=
ferred to as the =E2=80=9C<u><a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWF=
pbF9pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z1lEQUt2UktxclJLZ0dRVWZSaHhGdGcxVlFjNW5HWFpBOD0iLCJocmVmIj=
oiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuaG9sbHl3b29kcmVwb3J0ZXIuY29tL21vdmllcy9tb3ZpZS1mZWF0dXJlc=
y9hLXJhcmUtaW50ZXJ2aWV3LW1lZ2Fwcm9kdWNlci1hcm5vbi05MDQ5NDIvP3V0bV9jYW1wYWln=
bj1XaGF0K0klMjdtK0hlYXJpbmclMkIrLStTVUJTQ1JJQkVSUyslMjg2JTJGMjUlMkYyNCUyOVx=
1MDAyNnV0bV9jb250ZW50PVdoYXQrSSUyN20rSGVhcmluZyUyQistK1NVQlNDUklCRVJTKyUyOD=
YlMkY0JTJGMjQlMjlcdTAwMjZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsX2FjdGlvblx1MDAyNnV0bV9zb3VyY=
